source.name: E-Gov Travel (ETS) Measures
source.description: The Number of Vouchers Processed measure represents the number of vouchers processed by the three ETS vendors annually for the 24 largest Federal Civilian Agencies.  The % of Reservations Completed Online measure represents the percentage of reservations that are processed online versus manually by a travel agent.
